# Study logs — user only

**Never** read, write, list, or reference files under `work-log/study-logs/`.

Study logs are personal portfolio / learning notes for the repo owner. They are **not** part of `planningPhase`, `plan:gate`, or agent workflows.

Planning conversation audit → `work-log/planning/{NNN}_{date}_{time}_{slug}/audit-log.md` only.
